d.f: ￹￺name * title * designation￻名字，抬頭，命令，稱呼，名稱

e: ￹`Tadamaanay~ `ko~ `ngangan~ `nira~.￺He is a man of good reputation * above average intelligence.￻他的名聲很好
￹`Aka~ `pi~`tongangan~ `to~ `tamdaw~.￺Don't speak evil against the character of people.￻不要誹謗別人，不要說別人的壞話
￹`O~ `ci~`ngangan~`ay~ `cingra~ `to~ `tayal~.￺He has a reputation for his work.￻他是這一行的專家，他在他的工作崗位上很有名
￹`Pa~`ngangan~`en~ `koya~ `wawa~.￺Give that child a name.￻請為那孩子命名
